CGAL/SFCGAL dependency prefix.

Target triple: @TARGET_TRIPLE@
Target kind: @TARGET_KIND@
Boost version: @BOOST_VERSION@
GMP version: @GMP_VERSION@
MPFR version: @MPFR_VERSION@
CGAL version: @CGAL_VERSION@
SFCGAL version: @SFCGAL_VERSION@

This prefix is layered on top of the same-target Boost package and adds the
geometry dependencies used by PostGIS SFCGAL support. It intentionally does not
contain PostgreSQL, libpq, GDAL, GEOS, or PROJ.
